		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />All of them use lots of ticks and such, as for the most advanced, can't really tell unless you disassemble every game and grade them on "Quality of Code."
<br />
<br />
<br />And plus some mappers don't do anything extra, they just add more space. MMC3 has scanline, so that'd probably not count here, but do want MMC1 to count?
<br />
<br />As for no chips, I think the combo carts SMB/DH and SMB/WCTM/DH would win since they're the only ones without chips. And then there's the Gyromite with the converter without actual "chips." Haha.

		

