		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I can figure out two possible questions that could arise from this:
<br /><ul><li>What NROM games would most successfully fool the player into believing the board is more sophisticated than NROM? </li><li>What games using a discrete mapper or MMC1 would most successfully fool the player into believing the board is more sophisticated than discrete or MMC1? </li></ul>

		

